==English==
===Verb===
'''diminish'''  (''intransitive'' and ''transitive'')
# To make, or to become [[smaller]]
# To [[taper]]
#(''music'') To [[reduce]] a [[perfect]] or [[minor]] [[interval]] by a [[semitone]] 
